                            <comment id="17503841" author="jira-bot" created="Wed, 9 Mar 2022 20:49:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 48ab5e97e52a35676a90742732b247d1efb2f374 in logging-log4j2&apos;s branch refs/heads/release-2.x from Piotr P. Karwasz&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://gitbox.apache.org/repos/asf?p=logging-log4j2.git;h=48ab5e9&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://gitbox.apache.org/repos/asf?p=logging-log4j2.git;h=48ab5e9&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-3418&quot; title=&quot;Proper registration of Log4j2CloudConfigLoggingSystem&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LOG4J2-3418&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LOG4J2-3418&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; Fix Log4j2CloudConfigLoggingSystem registration&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This PR adds support for the `spring.factories` registration method of&lt;br/&gt;
the `Log4j2CloudConfigLoggingSystem` to replace the old Java system&lt;br/&gt;
properties injection method.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A Log4j 2.x `log4j2.disableCloudConfigLoggingSystem` property is added&lt;br/&gt;
to enable a choice between the `Log4j2CloudConfigLoggingSystem` and&lt;br/&gt;
`Log4j2LoggingSystem`.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17503856" author="pkarwasz" created="Wed, 9 Mar 2022 21:21:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=membersound&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;membersound&quot;&gt;membersound&lt;/a&gt;, I merged my PR and generated a snapshot for &lt;tt&gt;log4j-spring-boot&lt;/tt&gt;. Can you check if it solves your problem?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17512790" author="jira-bot" created="Sun, 27 Mar 2022 00:15:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 7ff07567f0f9b832b779bc7caf46878ac4918da1 in logging-log4j2&apos;s branch refs/heads/master from Piotr P. Karwasz&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://gitbox.apache.org/repos/asf?p=logging-log4j2.git;h=7ff0756&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://gitbox.apache.org/repos/asf?p=logging-log4j2.git;h=7ff0756&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-3418&quot; title=&quot;Proper registration of Log4j2CloudConfigLoggingSystem&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LOG4J2-3418&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LOG4J2-3418&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; Fix Log4j2CloudConfigLoggingSystem registration&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This PR adds support for the `spring.factories` registration method of&lt;br/&gt;
the `Log4j2CloudConfigLoggingSystem` to replace the old Java system&lt;br/&gt;
properties injection method.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A Log4j 2.x `log4j2.disableCloudConfigLoggingSystem` property is added&lt;br/&gt;
to enable a choice between the `Log4j2CloudConfigLoggingSystem` and&lt;br/&gt;
`Log4j2LoggingSystem`.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
